  <text>
      <body>
         <pb n="246"/>
         <div xml:id="orig_div1" xml:lang="eng" type="clericalNotes" rend="top centre"> 
            <p>Registered No. 1267 of <date calendar="#gregorian">1886</date></p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="orig_div2" xml:lang="ara" type="maintext">
            <p>
               <lb/>اقر
               <persName ref="#jamadi">جمادي</persName>
               سريح
               <persName ref="#saifbSultan">سيف بن سلطان</persName>
               ان عليه
               <persName ref="#mamlabNanji">لماملاه بن نانجي</persName>
               وكيل السركار ثمانية قروش صرف
               <lb/>البلد و قد باع له بحقه هذه بيته المبني بالحطب والطين الذي في ارض 
               <placeName ref="#bagamoyo">باجامويو</placeName>
               مجاور بيت 
               <lb/>جمادار
               <persName ref="#isaBalushi">عيسى بن كزية البلوشي</persName>
               بيعاً قطعاً تاريخ
               <date calendar="#hijri-qamri">يوم حادي في شهر القعدة سنة
               <num>١٢٩١</num></date>
               كتبه
               <lb/>الحقير الى ربه
               <persName ref="#abdullahbAli">عبدالله بن علي بن سالم بن عبدالسلام</persName>
               بيده و شهد بمعرفة جمادار
               <persName ref="#isaBalushi">عيسى بن كزية البلوشي</persName> 
               <lb/>و انا شاهده بذلك كتبه
               <persName ref="#nasserbSulaiman">ناصر بن سليمان</persName>
               بيده تاريخ ما تقدم
            </p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div2" corresp="#orig_div2">
            <p>
               <lb/><persName ref="#jamadi">Jamadi</persName>, the freed slave of <persName ref="#saifbSultan">Saif bin Sultan</persName>, acknowledges that he owes <persName ref="#mamlabNanji">Mamla bin Nanji</persName>, the agent of the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_sarkar">sarkar</ref>, <measure type="currency" unit="qirsh" quantity="8">eight <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_qirsh">qurush</ref></measure> in the currency
               <lb/>of the town, and he has sold him his house, made of timber and mud, that is at <placeName ref="#bagamoyo">Bagamoyo</placeName>, neighbouring the house of
               <lb/><ref type="glossary" target="#gl_jamadar">Jamadar</ref> <persName ref="#isaBalushi">Isa bin <unclear>Kuzya</unclear> Al-Balushi</persName>, [and this is] a complete sale on <date calendar="#hijri-qamri">the first of the month of Al-Qu‘da 1291</date>,<note>This is equivalent to 10 December 1874 CE.</note> and this was written by
               <lb/>the wretched for his Lord, <persName ref="#abdullahbAli">Abdullah bin Ali bin Salem bin Abdussalam</persName>, in his own hand, and it was witnessed with the knowledge of <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_jamadar">Jamadar</ref> <persName ref="#isaBalushi">Isa bin <unclear>Kuzya</unclear> Al-Balushi</persName>
               <lb/>and I am a witness to that, written by <persName ref="#nasserbSulaiman">Nasser bin Sulaiman</persName> by his own hand, on the aforementioned date.
            </p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="orig_div3" xml:lang="eng" type="clericalNotes" rend="middle centre">
            <p>
               <lb/>Dated <date calendar="#hijri-qamri">1st Elkadeh [Zu al-qaʿdah] 1291</date><note>This is written in line with the final line of the Arabic maintext above and refers to the date given in the copied deed.</note>
               <lb rend="empty"/>
               <lb/>Deed of Sale of a house at <placeName ref="#bagamoyo">Bagamoyo</placeName>
               <lb/>sold by <persName ref="#jamadi">Hamadi [Jamadi]</persName> <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_sarih">Soreeh [sarih]</ref> <persName ref="#saifbSultan">Saiff [Saif] bin Sultan</persName> for <measure type="currency" unit="qirsh" quantity="8">$8</measure>
               <lb/>to <persName ref="#mamlabNanji"><unclear>Mamla</unclear> bin Nanji</persName><note>"Mamla bin" is written in dark ink as a correction over some other text.</note> The Agent of <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_sarkar">Serkar [sarkar]</ref>
               <lb/>produced by <persName ref="#krishnadas">Kersendas [Krishnadas]</persName>
            </p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="orig_div4" xml:lang="eng" type="authorisation" rend="middle centre">
            <p>
               <placeName ref="#zanzibar">Zanzibar</placeName> <date calendar="#gregorian">29 December 1886</date> <persName ref="#ernestBerkeley">Ernest Berkeley</persName><note>This name is signed.</note> <choice><abbr>H. M.</abbr><expan>Her Majesty's</expan></choice> Vice Consul <placeName ref="#zanzibar">Zanzibar</placeName> <figure><figDesc>A small rectangle, containing the numbers 5/7. Below the box the words 'on Deed' are written.</figDesc></figure>
            </p>
         </div>
      </body>
